  "SOS report": "A single archive that automatically bundles Linux system logs and config for Red Hat support cases.",
  "static IP": "A manually fixed IP address that never changes, unlike a DHCP-assigned one.",
  "Virtual Media": "A feature that lets you mount an ISO file or USB drive on a physical server remotely, over the network.",
